Sturridge ya samu kwallo daga Xherdan Shaqiri a raga mai tsawon mita 30 a raga ta Chelsea, inda aka tashi 1-0.
Ya motsa kwallon zuwa gefen hagu kafin ya harbi hannun dama.
Sai jirgin ya tashi sama da jirgin da ke kusa da inda aka kafa tarun.
Ƙarƙashin ƙwallon ya ƙare a kan wani ƙwallon ƙafa na Kepa Arrizabalaga kuma ya shiga cikin raga.
"Ina kokarin shiga cikin matsayi, na shiga cikin kwallon, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna wasa a gaba a duk lokacin da zai yiwu, don haka ina kokarin samar da lokaci mai kyau", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
Na ga Kante yana zuwa, ya motsa kwallon, ban yi tunani sosai ba, sai kawai na yi ƙoƙari na harbi.
Chelsea ta ci gaba da ci 1-0 a wasan farko bayan da ta ci kwallo a minti na 25 daga hannun Eden Hazard.
Mai kula da blue ya sake mayar da kwallon zuwa Mateo Kovacic a wasan, kafin ya yi tsalle kuma ya shiga cikin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi saurin daya-biyu a tsakiya.
Daga nan sai ya buga kwallo mai kyau wanda ya jagoranci Hazard zuwa cikin fashewa.
Hazard ya gudu daga tsaron kuma ya buga raga a hannun hagu a gaban Liverpool Alisson Becker.
Liverpool za ta kara da Napoli a wasan rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai da za a yi a karfe 3 na yammacin ranar Laraba a filin wasa na San Paolo da ke birnin Napoli, Italiya.
Chelsea za ta buga wasan bidiyo a gasar Europa League da misalin karfe 3 na yammacin ranar Talata a birnin Landan.
