Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh
Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli ranar bikin auren bayan da kotun kolin ta yanke hukunci kan zargin Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin mata, Christine Blasey Ford, a cikin shekarun 1980s, a kan tashoshin talabijin shida.
A lokaci guda kuma, siyasa ta ci gaba da nuna rashin daidaito, yayin da ofisoshin suka yi watsi da al'ada a ranar Jumma'a a cikin wani abu da ba a zata ba a cikin minti na karshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi, don FBI ta gudanar da bincike kan zargin a cikin mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa kotun dattijai cewa ba ta da wata shakka cewa Kavanaugh ya bugu kuma ya yi ƙoƙari ya fitar da ita zuwa wani taron dalibai.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ta fi dacewa, ya ce ba shi da shakka cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Gaskiya ne, fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne Nielsen ya ce sun gani a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige matsakaicin adadin kuɗi a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a kai tsaye ba ne ga wasu tashoshin watsa labarai da suka san shi, kamar PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yana da matsala wajen kirga yawan mutanen da ke kallon ofisoshin.
Don kwatanta, wannan ita ce irin wannan taron kamar kallon wasan kwallon kafa a wasan karshe ko kuma kyautar Academy Awards.
Kafofin watsa labarai na Fox News, wadanda masu gabatar da su suka tallafawa nadin Kavanaugh, sun kasance a saman dukkan tashoshin watsa labarai, tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a yayin shari'ar da ta dauki tsawon yini, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ya biyo baya da miliyan 3.26 na masu kallo.
CBS ta samu dala miliyan 3.1, NBC ta samu dala miliyan 2.94, MSNBC ta samu dala miliyan 2.89 da kuma CNN ta samu dala miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
Mutane sun yi ɗokin ganin an yi musu shari'a.
Flake ne babban jarumin wannan abin da ya faru a ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da jam'iyyar Republican ta sanar da cewa za ta kada kuri'a ga Kavanaugh, an ga shi a ranar Jumma'a da safe da CNN da CBS suka yi yayin da masu zanga-zanga ke ihu a kansa yayin da yake kokarin shiga wani lif don shari'ar kotu.
Bai kalli sama ba, yayin da aka gano shi na tsawon mintuna da yawa, kai tsaye akan CNN.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
Kuna zaton yana faɗin gaskiya ne a madadin ƙasar?
Sai wani ya ce masa, "Kai mai ƙarfi ne, gama mata da yawa ba su da ƙarfi".
Flake ya ce gwamnatinsa ta sanar da shi kafin tashin jirgin ya daina cewa yana da karin bayani ga kwamitin.
Kafofin watsa labarai sun watsa shirye-shiryen ne sa'o'i kadan bayan haka, lokacin da kotun ta yanke shawarar tura nadin Kavanaugh zuwa majalisar dattijai don jefa kuri'a.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan ya san cewa FBI za ta binciki tuhumar da aka yi wa wanda aka zaba kafin mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda wani mai gabatar da kara na 'yan Democrat ya ce.
Flake ya kasance mai amincewa da wasu daga cikin tattaunawar da abokinsa, Sanata na Democrat, Chris Coons.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu sanatoci daga baya, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Zaɓen Flake ya kasance mai ƙarfi, saboda a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba su da kuri'un da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya fara binciken FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
Firaministar Birtaniya May ta zargi 'yan majalisa da 'yin wasa da siyasa' kan batun Brexit
Firayim Minista Theresa May ta zargi 'yan adawa da shirin ta na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai da yin wasa da siyasar makomar Burtaniya, da kuma bata sha'awar al'umma, a wata hira da jaridar Sunday Times.
Firaministar Birtaniya Theresa May, tana halartar taron jam'iyyar Conservative a birnin Birmingham, a ranar 29 ga watan Satumbar 2018.
A wata hira da aka yi da ita a shafin farko na jaridar, tsohon sakataren harkokin wajenta, Boris Johnson, ya jaddada shirin da ta kira Chequers na Brexit, yana mai cewa shawarar da Birtaniya da EU za su yi na karbar haraji daga juna "ba daidai ba ne".
Harbin Wayde Sims: 'Yan sanda sun kama Dyteon Simpson a kan zargin mutuwar dan wasan LSU.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargi da harbin Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwallo mai shekaru 20 a LSU.
Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, an kama shi kuma an yi masa rajistar kisa, in ji 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge.
Masu aikin sun aika da hotuna na haɗuwa tsakanin Sims da Simpson, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a cikin rikici.
'Yan sanda sun gano tabarau a wurin kuma sun ce sun sami DNA na Simpson a kansu, in ji kamfanin CBS, WAFB.
Bayan da aka yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yarda da harbi da kisan Wayde.
An biya kudin belin na dala 350,000, in ji mai gabatar da kara.
Ofishin kula da lafiyar mutane na The East Baton Rouge ya fitar da wani rahoto na farko a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce dalilin mutuwar shi ne raunukan da aka yi wa kansa da kuma wuyansa.
Ma'aikatar ta ba da lada ga 'yar tseren' yan sanda na Louisiana, Cibiyar Binciken Laifuka ta Jihar, 'yan sanda na Jami'ar Southern da mazauna yankin don taimakawa wajen binciken da ya kai ga kama.
Daraktan wasanni na LSU, Joe Alleva, ya gode wa 'yan sanda na yankin saboda "kusawarsu da kuma son adalci".
Sims yana da shekara ashirin.
Mai tsayi 201 cm ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa Wayne ya buga wasan ƙwallon ƙafa na LSU.
Ya samu 5.6 da 2.6 rebounds a kowace wasa a kakar wasa ta karshe.
A ranar Jumma'a, kocin LSU, Will Wade, ya ce kungiyar ba ta da wani abu kuma ta firgita da mutuwar Wayde.
"Wannan shi ne abin da kuke damuwa akai-akai", in ji Wade.
Dutsen mai fitad da wuta yana zubo ruwan sama a birnin Mexico
Fashewar toka daga dutsen Popocatepetl yana da dare ga yankunan kudancin babban birnin Mexico.
A ranar Asabar, dokar hana fita ta hana Mexico daga cikin dutsen bayan da aka fara aiki a cikin gosop kuma an yi rikodin 183 na gas da ash a cikin sa'o'i 24.
Sai aka yi tsawa da aradu, aka yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa.
Hotunan 'yan sanda na kasar ta Ostiraliya a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna yadda 'yan sanda ke ajiye motoci a wani unguwa da ke birnin Mexico, wanda yanzu ake kira Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin kasa sun gano karuwar ayyukan dutsen mai fitad da wuta mai nisan mil 45 (72 km) daga babban birnin kasar bayan wata girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.1 ta afku a tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Dutsen mai fitad da wuta, wanda aka sani da Don Goyo ya kasance yana aiki tun 1994.
'Yan sanda sun yi rikici da' yan Catalonia masu neman 'yanci, kafin ranar tunawa da zaben.
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan masu zanga-zangar neman sakin sun yi karo da 'yan sanda, kuma dubban mutane sun yi zanga-zanga a filin wasa don tunawa da ranar farko ta zaben fidda gwani.
Wasu 'yan gudun hijira da aka yi wa lakabi da masu rufe fuska, da aka hana su daga yin amfani da miyagun kwayoyi, sun yi amfani da ƙwai da kuma man fetur don su bi su, suna jiran duhu a tituna, wanda ya kasance mai yawa ga masu tafiya.
Daga baya, an sake yin faɗa, kuma an tilasta wa 'yan sanda su yi amfani da sandunansu don su dakatar da faɗa.
A tsawon sa'o'i, kungiyoyin 'yanci sun yi waka ba tare da manta ba, ba tare da gafartawa ba, suna cewa "Ba za ku rayu a Spain ba" da kuka na 'yan jam'iyyar.
An yi wa mutane 14 magani don rashin rauni daga tashin hankalin, wanda aka ba da rahoto ga 'yan jarida a wurin.
An ci gaba da samun tashin hankali a cikin jam'iyyar 'yanci, shekara guda bayan da Madrid ta yi watsi da kuri'ar raba gardamar ranar 1 ga watan Oktoba, amma 'yan Catalonia masu neman' yanci sun yi murna.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun fi son zama masu zaman kansu, duk da cewa rashin rinjaye ya kasance kadan, saboda waɗanda ke adawa da 'yanci sun fi yawan yin watsi da zaben.
A cewar hukumomin Catalonia, kusan mutane 1,000 ne aka kwashe a bara, bayan da 'yan sanda, a cikin rikice-rikice masu yawa, suka yi ƙoƙarin dakatar da zaben a wuraren zabe a duk faɗin ƙasar.
Wasu 'yan bindiga sun kafa tanti a daren ranar Juma'a don su hana 'yan sanda yin zanga-zanga.
Amma, sai magabcin ya bi wata hanya dabam.
Narcis Termes, mai shekaru 68, wani mai aikin lantarki wanda ya yi adawa da masu neman 'yanci tare da matarsa, ya ce ba shi da bege game da yadda Catalonia za ta rabu da ita.
A shekarar da ta gabata mun fuskanci lokaci mafi kyau.
"Na ga iyayena suna kuka saboda farin ciki, domin ba su da damar yin zabe, amma yanzu muna cikin damuwa", in ji shi.
Duk da nasarar da suka samu, ko da yake kadan, a zaben da aka yi a watan Disamba, jam'iyyun 'yanci na Catalonia sun yi watsi da ci gaba da nunawa a wannan shekara, inda yawancin shugabannin su ke gudun hijira, ko kuma suna tsare da jiran su a gaban kotu saboda rawar da suka taka wajen shirya zaben raba gardama da kuma barazanar da ta biyo baya.
Joan Puig, wani mai aikin injiniya mai shekaru 42, wanda ya yi rikodin zanga-zangar ta wayar salula don tallafawa 'yan sanda, ya ce' yan siyasa a bangarorin biyu sun nuna rashin amincewarsu.
Ya ce, "Zai ƙara tsanani".
A ranar Asabar daya daga cikin shugabannin Catalonia tara da ke tsare tun a karshen shekarar da ta gabata, Oriol Junqueras ya sanar da cewa zai tsaya takarar zama dan majalisar Turai a shekara mai zuwa.
"Yin takara a zaben Turai shine hanya mafi kyau don nuna rashin amincewa da koma baya a cikin dabi'un dimokiradiyya da kuma zalunci da muka gani daga gwamnatin Spain", in ji shi.
