Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron da za a yi a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shine taron farko na biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, tare da wasu wuraren da za a yi masa ziyara a Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da ake neman zabensa don cike gurbin da ake da shi a kotun kolin, Trump zai gina goyon baya a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump a West Virginia a daren yau kuma yaya kake kallon intanet?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a YouTube a ƙasa.
Da alama Trump zai tattauna batun shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli a wannan makon, lamarin da ya taso sakamakon zargin cin zarafin jima'i, inda aka dakatar da wani hukunci na majalisar dattijai na tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron shine don taimakawa 'yan Republican su yi zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, tawagar Trump ta sanar da cewa za a yi zaman biyar a mako mai zuwa domin karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kara yawan su a majalisar dattijai da wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Shugaban kasa yana da matukar muhimmanci ga jadawalin taronsa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya yayin da muke gab da wani gaggawa", in ji wani kakakin Trump wanda ya ƙi bayyana sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters.
Taron na takwas da za a yi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling a wannan yammacin zai iya tara magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya sami labarin kafofin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana neman taimakon dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Republican a West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke neman zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban zai zo ya tallafa masa a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
