A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen Festival zai tara dubban mutane da za su taru a kan babban filin shakatawa na Central Park, ba kawai don ganin wasan kwaikwayon daga Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don haskaka ainihin manufar wannan taron, don kawo ƙarshen talauci mai tsanani kafin 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani shiri ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta ta duniya wadda ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun damar shiga kyauta (sai dai idan kuna son biyan kuɗin VIP), masu halarta dole ne su yi aiki da wasu ayyuka, ko ayyuka kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, kira, ko yin wani abu mai mahimmanci don taimakawa wajen haskakawa game da ƙarshen talauci.
