Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwa a matsayin wata hanya ta hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Cikin Gida
Washington na iya amfani da dakarun sojin ruwa idan ya cancanta don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwannin, gami da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya nakalto.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa ayyukan Rasha a Siriya - musamman ma inda aka ba da izini daga gwamnatin da ke da doka - wani abu ne na farko don gano sababbin kasuwannin makamashi.
Ina ganin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine don su sayar da makamashi, kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, mafi kyawun cibiyar Turai, bayan duk, ya ce.
Kuma bisa ga jami'an, akwai hanyoyi da dama da za a bi da shi.
"Amurka tana da ikon, tare da sojojinmu, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin jiragen ruwa suna buɗe kuma idan ya cancanta, hana su don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba zai shiga kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga taron a wani taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta yi, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ake kira 'Speech of the Energy Consumer' a Amurka.
Ya fara kwatanta hanyoyin da Washington ke bi da Rasha da Iran, yana mai jaddada cewa suna da kama da juna.
"Dole ne tattalin arzikin Iran da Rasha su kasance, a mafi yawancin, masu iko da kuma musayar man fetur", in ji shi, yana nuna Rasha a matsayin kasa mai amfani da abu daya, kuma tana da alaƙa da tattalin arziki da man fetur.
Wadannan maganganun sun zo ne a lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ta yi niyyar kara fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, maimakon Rasha, wanda shine mafi kyawun zaɓi ga masu amfani da Turai.
A wannan bangaren, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, sun yi kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun mai na Nord Stream 2, wanda a cewar Trump, ya mayar da Berlin "kurkuku" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta yi nuni a kai a kai cewa aikin famfo na Nord Stream 2, wanda ya kai dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka girman aikin da ake yi yanzu zuwa biliyan 110, ba komai bane face aikin kudi.
Kremlin ya ce, Washington ta nuna adawa da wannan shiri ne kawai saboda dalilai na kudi, kuma wannan misali ne na rashin gasa.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki ba don rage matsin lamba kuma masu amfani su zabi masu karɓar bakuncin su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Alexander Novak, a wani taro da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Wannan halin da Amurka ta nuna ya sa Jamus ta yi matukar damuwa, saboda ta sake yin la'akari da alhakin aikin.
Babban kamfanin masana'antu na Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ya bukaci Amurka ta guje wa manufofin samar da makamashi na ST, ciki har da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wani ɓangare na uku ya shiga cikin samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), a wani taron da aka yi tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus, Angela Merkel, da shugaban Rasha, Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren Za Ta Yi Tunanin Tsayawa Takarar Shugaban Kasa A 2020, In Ji Sanatan Massachusetts
Sanata daga Massachusetts, Elizabeth Warren, ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi la'akari da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron da aka yi a majalisar dokoki a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta bayyana cewa tana tunanin yin takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su fahimci gazawar gwamnati, kuma hakan na nufin mata masu matsayi a kan kujerun gwamnati", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
A daren 6 ga watan Nuwamba zan yi la'akari da ko zan tsaya takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya bayyana ra'ayinsa game da shugaban kasar Donald Trump a majalisar dattijai, yana mai cewa ya yi mulkin kasar a kan madaidaiciyar hanya.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya yi ta sukar Trump, kuma wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, ya fito fili.
A wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter ranar Juma'a, Warren ya rubuta "A zahiri muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin zaben".
A ranar bikin aure, an sanar da wani rahoto na zaben, wanda ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'a na Warren sun yi imanin cewa ba za ta yi takara a 2020 ba.
Kashi talatin da biyar cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce Sanatan ba zai yi takara ba, a cewar binciken Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari sun goyi bayan wannan ra'ayi.
Sanarwar zaben ta nuna cewa goyon baya ya fi yawa ga wani shiri na tsohon gwamna, Deval Patrick, tare da kashi 38 cikin dari a cikin wani shiri da kashi 48 cikin dari.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da aka ambata a matsayin masu neman takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa, Joe Biden, da Sanata daga Vermont, Bernie Sanders.
