Girgizar kasa da ambaliyar ruwa a Indonesia
Aƙalla mutane 384 ne girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa suka kashe a birnin Indonesiya na Pau a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ƙaru.
Tare da rashin hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su sami wata sanarwa daga gwamnatin Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa, wanda ya auna 7.5 a kan ma'aunin Richter.
An kwashe mutane fiye da dubu goma sha shida daga birnin Bulus bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawest:
Palu babban birni ne na yankin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda yawan jama'arsa a shekarar 2017 ya kai 379,800.
A shekara ta arba'in, an yi bikin ranar da aka yi girgizar ƙasa kuma aka yi ambaliyar ruwa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a bakin tekun tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin gwamnati, wanda a zahiri ƙasa ɗaya ce, yawan jama'a ya kai 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan kayan aikin tattalin arzikin yankin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, ma'adinai na ma'adinai suna da muhimmanci a cikin ƙasa, amma an fi tara su a Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da ambaliyar ruwa mai tsanani a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996 kuma wata guguwar tsunami ta afku a Yammacin Gabas inda ta kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific da ke fama da girgizar kasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar kasa da ambaliyar ruwa a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan:
2004: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin yankin Indonesiya, Aceh, a Arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane sama da 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A jerin manyan girgizar asa buga yammacin Coast na Sumatra a karshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudu maso gabashin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya fashe a gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin yankin yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mentawai, a wajen Sumatra, inda ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya lalata kauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gwamnatin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da tsoro, yayin da mutane ke tunawa da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu wata ambaliyar ruwa da ta faru a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu daga gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na kasar Indonesia inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon bude ido su yi zaman kashe wando.
