Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 tare da nasara a kan Team Amurka, wanda ya kammala 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kambin, lokacin da tawagar Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata don lashe Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka, Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi fama da mafi yawan gasar, ya buga wasan farko a rami na 16, inda ya kasance 3, a cikin ruwa, kuma ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
